hadiths[65]{hadithnumber,text}:
3371,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujhey merey khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nasihat kartey huye farmaya : sharab na peena kyonkey wo har burai ki kunji hai."
3372,"Hazrat Khubab bin Arat (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sharab sey perhez karo. uska gunah (doosrey tamam) gunahon sey isi tarah badh kar hai jis tarah uska paudaa darakhton sey buland hai (angoor ki bail jis darkht par chadhti hai, us sey buland nazar aati hai)."
3373,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs duniya mein sharab piye ga, wo aakhirat mein nahin pi sakeyga, siwaye is surat key ke wo (sharab noshi sey) tauba kar ley."
3374,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs duniya mein sharab piye ga , wo aakhirat mein nahin pi sakeyga."
3375,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamesha sharab peeney wala , but poojney waley ki tarah hai."
3376,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamesha sharab peeney wala jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga."
3377,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney sharab pi aur usey nasha ho gaya, uski chaalis din tak namaz qubul nahin hogi. aur agar wo (tauba kiye baghair) mar gaya to jahannam mein dakhil hoga. agar usney tauba ki to Allah uski tauba qubul farmaeyga. agar usney dobara sharab pi li aur usey nasha ho gaya to uski namaz (mazeed) chaalis din qubul nahin hogi. agar (us asnaa mein) wo (tauba kiye baghair) mar gaya to jahannam mein dakhil hoga. aur agar tauba kar li to Allah uski tauba qubul farmaeyga. agar phir (teesri baar) sharab pi aur usey nasha ho gaya to uski namaz (mazeed) chaalis din tak qubul nahin hogi. agar wo mar gaya to jahannam mein dakhil hoga. aur agar tauba kar li to Allah uski tauba qubul farmaeyga. agar usney phir (chauthi baar) sharab pi to Allah Taala ney (aisey shakhs key barey mein) pukhta faisla kar liya hai ke usey qiyamat key din gandi keechad pilaaeyga. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! gandi keechad sey kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jahannamiyon ki peep aur gandagi."
3378,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sharab in do nabatat sey banti hai : khajoor aur angoor."
3379,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gehun ki sharab hoti hai, jau ki sharab hoti hai, munaqqaa sey (bani hui nasha aawar chiz) sharab hoti hai, khushk khajoor sey (bani hui nasha aawar chiz) sharab hoti hai aur shehad sey (bani hui nasha aawar chiz) sharab hoti hai."
3380,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sharab mein das tareh par lanat ki gaee hai : khud us (sharab) ki zaat par , is ko nichodne waley (ras nichod kar sharab bananey waley) par, nichudwaane waley (sharab banwaane waley) par, iskey bechney waley par , iskey kharidney waley par iskey uthaney waley par, jis key paas ley jaaey jaey us par, iski qeemat khaney waley par, isey peeney waley par aur iskey pilaney waley par."
3381,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sharab sey mutalliq das afrad par lanat farmaai hai : isey nichodne waley par , nichudwaane wala , jis key liye nichodi gaee , isey utha kar ley janey waley par , jis key liye utha kar ley jaai gaee , isey bechney waley par , jis key liye bechi gaee , isey pilaney waley par , aur jisey pilai gaee yahan tak key unhoney is tarah key das afrad shumar kiye."
3382,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab sood key barey mein Sura Baqra key akheer wali aayaat nazil huin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghar sey) bahar tashrif ley gaey aur sharab ki tijarat key haram honey ka aelan farma diya."
3383,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko ittilaa mili ke Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ney sharab farokht ki hai to unhoney farmaya : Allah Taala Samura ko tabah karey. kya usey malum nahin tha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala yahudiyon par lanat nazil farmaaey ! un par charbi haram ki gaee to unhoney usey pighla kar bech diya."
3384,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat din ka nizam khatam nahin hoga yahan tak key meri ummat key kuchh log sharab piyegey lekin usey uskey naam (sharab) key siwa doosrey naam sey pukarengey."
3385,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat key kuchh log sharab ko apna rakha huwa doosra naam dey kar pi leingey."
3386,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis mashrub sey nasha aaye wo haram hai."
3387,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha aawar chiz haram hai."
3388,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha aawar chiz haram hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : ye ehale Misr ki hadees hai."
3389,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha aawar chiz har momin par haram hai. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : ) ye Ruqaa walon ki hadees hai."
3390,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha aawar chiz sharab hai, aur har sharab haram hai."
3391,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha aawar chiz haram hai."
3392,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har nasha aawar chiz haram hai. aur jis chiz ki ziyada miqdaar sey nasha aaye , uski thodi miqdaar bhi haram hai."
3393,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis chiz ki ziyada miqdaar sey nasha aaye , uski thodi miqdaar bhi haram hai."
3394,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis chiz ki ziyada miqdaar sey nasha aaye, uski thodi miqdaar bhi haram hai."
3395,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khajuren aur munaqqaa mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya : aur neem pukhta (adhpaki) khajuren aur taza pakki hui khajuren mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney ye riwayat Ata bin Abi Ribah Makki key wastey sey bhi sabiqa hadees ki misl (tarah) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan ki hai.
3396,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khushk khajuron aur neem pukhta (adhpaki) khajuron ko mila kar nabeez na banao. dono mein sey har eik ki alehda alehda nabeez bana liya karo."
3397,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Haris bin Rabaee Sulami Ansari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : taza paki hui khajuron aur neem pukhta (adhpaki) (gadar) khajuron ko (nabeez bananey key liye)  ikhatta na karo, aur na munaqqaa aur khushk khajoor ko milaao. in mein sey har eik ki nabeez juda juda bana lo."
3398,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye mishkeezey mein nabeez banaya kartey they. hum mutthi bhar khushk khajuren ya mutthi bhar munaqqaa ley kar us (mishkeezey) mein dal detey, phir is par (hasabe zarurat) pani dal detey. hum subh key waqt bhigotey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sham ko pi letey aur Sham ko bhigotey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subah ko usey pi letey. Abu-Muaawia (apni riwayat mein ye alfaz) bayan kartey hain.  hum din ko bhigotey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko pi letey, ya raat ko bhigotey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) din ko pi letey."
3399,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye nabeez tayyar ki jati thi. aap isey us din bhi nosh farmatey aur doosrey teesrey din bhi. phir agar (teesrey din) is mein sey kuch bach jati to isey gira detey ya aap key hukm sey isey gira diya jata."
3400,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye patthar key eik bartan mein nabeez tayyar ki jati thi."
3401,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney lakdi key bartan mein , taar-kol lagey bartan mein , kadu sey baney huye bartan (taunbey) mein aur sabz (harae) roghani ghadey mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya. aur farmaya : har nasha aawar chiz haram hai."
3402,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney taar-kol lagey bartan mein aur kaddu sey baney huye bartan (tonbe) mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya.
3403,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney roghani ghadey mein, kaddu sey baney huye bartan mein aur lakdi sey baney huye bartan mein peeney sey mana farmaya."
3404,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yaamar (Daili) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kaddu sey baney huye bartan aur roghani ghadey (mein nabeez bananey) sey mana farmaya."
3405,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhein kuchh bartanon sey mana kiya tha, ab un mein nabeez bana liya karo, aur har nasha aawar mashrub sey perhez karo."
3406,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhein (kuchh) bartanon mein bani hui nabeez sey mana kiya tha. suno ! bartan kisi chiz ko haram nahin karta. (albatta) har nasha aawar chiz haram hai."
3407,"Ummul-mominin Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : kya koi aurat aisey nahin kar sakti ke har saal apney qurbani key janwer ki khaal sey mishkeeza bana liya kerey? (aurton ko ye kaam karna chahiye). phir farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney matkey mein aur falan falan chiz mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya hai, albatta sirka rakha ja sakta hai."
3408,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney matkon mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya hai."
3409,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ghadey mein bani hui nabeez pesh ki gaee jis mein ubaal paida ho gaya tha (aur jhaag aa gaya tha). aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey deewar par dey maaro. ye to aisey shakhs ka mashrub hai jo Allah par aur aakhirat key din par eman nahin rakhta.
3410,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bartan dhanp diya karo, mishkeezey ka munh baandh diya karo, chiragh bujha diya karo aur darwaza band kar diya karo kyonkey shetan (munh band) mushk ko nahin kholta, darwaza nahin kholta aur (dhaanpey huye) bartan ko nahin kholta. agar kisi ko bartan par rakhney key liye lakdi (darkht ki patli shaakh waghera) key siwa kuchh na miley to usey hi Allah ka naam ley kar rakh dey. (chiragh bujha diya karo) isliye ke nanhi shareer chuhiyaa ghar ko aag laga kar (ghar ko ya ghar walon ko) jala deti hai."
3411,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen bartan dhaanpney ka, mushk ka munh baandhney ka aur bartan ondhey kar key rakhney ka hukm diya ."
3412,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main raat ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye (pani key) teen bartan dhanp kar rakhti thi . eik bartan aap key istinja key liye , eik bartan aap ki miswak (aur wuzu) key liye aur eik bartan aap key peeney key liye ."
3413,"ummul-mominin sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs chaandi key bartan mein (pani ya koi aur mashrub) peeta hai, wo apney pet mein jahannam ki aag ghat-ghat dal raha hai."
3414,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney soney aur chaandi key bartanon mein peeney sey mana farmaya, aur farmaya : wo duniya mein un (kafiron) key liye hain aur aakhirat main tumharey liye ."
3415,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs chaandi key bartan mein peeta hai, wo apney pet mein jahannam ki aag ghat-ghat dal raha hai."
3416,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai key wo bartan mein teen baar saans letey they. aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bartan mein teen baar saans letey they.
3417,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (pani) piya to is mein do baar saans liya .
3418,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mishkeezon key munh ooper ki taraf mod kar unkey munhon sey pani peeney sey mana farmaya.
3419,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mishkeezon key munh ooper ki taraf mod kar unkey munhon sey pani peeney sey mana farmaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mumaaniat key baad eik aadmi raat ko utha aur usney (pani peeney key liye) mishkeezey ka munh ultaya to is mein sey sanp nikal aaya ."
3420,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mishkeezey key munh sey pani peeney sey mana farmaya."
3421,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya ke mashk key munh sey pani piya jaey .
3422,Imam Shaaby (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat ki ke unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko zamzam ka pani pesh kya to aap ney khadey khadey pi liya . Shaaby (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : mainey ikrima (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye hadees sunai to unhoney Allah ki qism kha kar farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aisey nahin kya.
3423,"Hazrat Kabsha ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey yahan tashrif ley gaey . unkey paas eik mashk latki hui thi, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey ho kar us sey pani pi liya. Kabsha (Raziallahu anha) Raziallahu anha ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key dehne-Mubarak ki barkat key khayal sey mashk ka munh kaat liya ."
3424,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey ho kar peeney sey mana farmaya.
3425,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein doodh pesh kya gaya jis mein pani milaaya gaya tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key daain taraf eik earaab sahabi they aur baain taraf abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney pi kar eeraabi sahabi ko ata kya aur farmaya : daain taraf wala ( ziyada haq daar hai) , phir uskey baad ka daain taraf wala ."
3426,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein doodh pesh kya gaya . aap ki daain taraf Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) they aur baain taraf Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey farmaya : kya tum mujhey ijazat detey ho ke main Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ko peeney ko dun? , 'Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : main to Allah key Rasool ka jutha apney sey pehley kisi ko dena pasand nahin karta. chunanche Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney ley kar (doodh) piya, aur (un key baad) Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ney piya ."
3427,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs (pani waghera) piye to usey bartan mein saans nahin lena chahiye . agar dobara peena chahey to bartan ( munh sey) hataaey , phir chahey to dobara (mazid) pi ley ."
3428,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bartan mein saans leney sey mana farmaya."
3429,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney peeney ki chiz mein phunk maarney sey mana farmaya."
3430,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peeney ki chiz mein phunk nahin maara kartey they."
3431,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen pet key bal (let kar) pani peeney sey mana farmaya hai, isi ko kraa kehtey hain. aur hamein eik haath sey chullu mein pani leney sey mana kiya hai aur farmaya : koi shakhs is tarah zaban nikal kar pani na piye, jis tarah kutta zaban sey pani peeta hai, na is tarah eik haath sey pani piye , jis tarah wo log peetey hain jin sey Allah naraz hai, aur na raat ko kisi bartan mein pani piye jab tak usey harkat na dey ley, siwaye iskey ke bartan dhakaa huwa ho. aur jo shakhs inkisaar ki niyat sey haath sey (chullu bhar kar) pani peeta hai, halanke usey bartan mil sakta hai, Allah Taala uskey liye uski ungliyon ki tadaad key mutabiq nekiyan likh deta hai. ye (haathon ki lap) Esa ibn Maryam (Aleh.) ka bartan tha. jab unhoney ye keh kar piyala phenk diya tha : uff ! ye bhi duniya ka saman hai."
3432,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik Ansari key paas tashrif ley gaey. wo sahab apney baagh mein (darakhton waghera ko) pani dey rahey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : agar tumharey paas raat ka mishkeezey mein pada huwa pani hai to hamen pila do warna hum (behtey pani sey) munh laga kar pi leingey. unhoney kaha : merey paas pani hai jo raat ka mushk mein rakha huwa hai, chunanche wo Sahabi chal padey. unkey sath hum bhi chhappar mein chaley gaey. unhoney raat ko mishkeezey mein rakhey huye pani main eik bakri ka doodh doh kar mila diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney piya, phir us (Ansari Sahabi) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath aaney waley ko bhi isi tarah doodh wala pani pesh kiya."
3433,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum eik taalaab key paas sey guzrey to us sey munh laga kar pani peeney lagey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munh laga kar pani na piyo lekin apney haath dho lo aur un mein ley kar pani piyo kyonkey haath sey ziyada pakizah koi bartan nahin."
3434,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ko pani pilaney wala aakhir mein piya karta hai."
3435,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas shishey ka eik piyala tha. aap is mein (pani waghera) piya kartey they.
